{
  "stem": "27340.5",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "By that time, I must have been about 25, 26, something of that nature, yes.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] there-- we, the building-- building this factory was fascinating because we got all the machinery as presents from various organizations throughout the world.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the biggest headache was that there were all these machines, some of them quite complex for those days, nothing like machine tools are today with computer control and so on.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But nevertheless, complex for those days and had to be assembled.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And very often, certain parts were missing where you had to sort of figure out how does that get together with that.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They were fundamentally all surplus war equipment, mainly from the United States, from the United Kingdom, from Italy, and from France.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And one of my tasks, particularly, was to try and assemble these machines, not entirely on my own.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We had-- we had a complement of about 180 craftsmen there from all over the world, incidentally.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "All Jewish, but not necessarily always a common language.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But in engineering, this is not too difficult, because you can always sketch things, your ideas and so on and so forth.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So that really presented no problem.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Language was a problem when you were involved in some combat, and the combat unit.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, I was trying for that in case there were any other conflagrations, short periods of war.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I was never involved in any major campaign, such as, for instance, the Six Day War or-- or-- or perhaps the, you know, the-- the-- the Battle of the Suez Canal, and so on.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "By that time, I was long out of the country again.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I came back to England again.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I didn't settle in Israel for a very, very good reason.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
